this is what 25 looks like but not really. 25 looks like kissing my partner goodnight & going for long walks for fun. 25 means baking for my family & making my sister laugh. 25 means picking up a paint brush again & actually finishing said painting. 25 means finding my personal style & learning how to tame my wild hair. 25 means canceling my subscription to perfection & just trying. I was going to say something about loving myself but 25 is more than that and shouldn’t be whittled down to my cellulite & tummy rolls. It’s so much more than that.
evening walkies are literally my favorite thing in the world  #plussize #curve #eveningstroll #workoutset #curlyhair

In 2024 may your ass look like a disco ball, may your wine glass always be full, may you have abundance showered on you endlessly, may you sleep 10 hours a night, may you find your soulmate, may you hit the mute button & may you find your art! I love you! Keep becoming more yourself, (whatever that means for you)! 2024 will be more than you could’ve wished. Quantum physics is on our sides girlypops! 💅🏻💸🪩💖🦋

Happy 1 Year Anniversary to my sweetest husband!!! One year has flown by so quickly. I am so obsessed with you!! If this is what one year feels like then I better not blink from now on. It was nothing but nonstop laughs. I get to have the best partner & best friend. Each year with you just gets sweeter and sweeter. Everyday feels like a holiday with you. I am the luckiest girl because I have you. Here’s to our honeymoon phase never, ever ending. 🥂✨🥵 @jaackmasters
One perfect year with my beanfrog. 🫶🏼 #marriage #anniversary
